  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic, ginger, and lemongrass; cook until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add Thai cherry tomatoes, fish sauce, brown sugar, soy sauce, and chili flakes; cook for 3-4 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in lime juice and rice vinegar.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a dolset stone bowl and garnish with fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately, as the tomatoes will shatter upon contact with the bowl.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro, if desired."
  ],
